{"tid":2222604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"孕婦遭防暴拉跌　鄧炳強：當時現場嘈吵事後警員已慰問","createTime":"2020-09-29T08:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-29T11:25:48.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"ff7373d4cb2fb415490af7773f0ea802bd3b4642","tid":2222604,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】警務處處長鄧炳強出席油尖旺區議會會議，有團體到場支持警方執法。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強到旺角政府合署，出席油尖旺區議會會議，並向在場支持者揮手及接受獻花，多名軍裝警員則在政府合署一帶駐守。<br />\n<br />\n他在區議會上回應早前有孕婦在旺角的驅散行動中，被防暴警察拉跌，指當時現場嘈吵，事發後警員已上前慰問，又指相關個案已有人投訴，不便評論。<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強：「的確現場曾有人叫過有孕婦在此，亦有人叫喊其他不同的口號，現場非常嘈雜和混亂，相信並非所有在場人士能夠聽到所有人說的所有說話。當時現場有人作出擾亂公眾秩序的行為，所以要進行拘捕行動；過程中被捕人士的懷孕妻子跌倒在地上，發現這個情況下，有女同事立刻照顧和安慰她，並馬上安排到醫院檢查。」"},{"pid":"53f17f09bf2f0a80520a40ffcbd956cbd66a7308","tid":2222604,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:03:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=407323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407323&d=3%2F9Bgz%2Fikyxb3M9FpachXHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=44aedc54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D407323&h=d3e1da8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=407323</a>"},{"pid":"0d6f8b86d08155f3338579c152521f27a14c0296","tid":2222604,"uid":294182,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:04:39.000Z","msg":"PK真係有樣睇"},{"pid":"4877837098b81caddf7a4c42c1eb0e62a038250b","tid":2222604,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:05:37.000Z","msg":"人渣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dbd556874d1fd90d34fedc4466fedc4f0780b5","tid":2222604,"uid":38666,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-29T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"又話不便評論<br />\n但又話已上前慰問<br 